LATEST PRINCE HARRY NEWS PLUS DUKE OF SUSSEX'S BABY UPDATES

Prince Harry slammed for 'snubbing the Queen' (again) A spokesperson for Harry on Friday confirmed he would not be leaving his Montecito mansion to attend his grandfather's Service of Thanksgiving. Prince Harry slammed for snubbing the Queen (again)

Meghan Markle UNFILTERED: Marrying Prince Harry launched her into superstardom, but these photos reveal the royal moments we rarely see From romantic scenes and sweet smiles to contemptuous glances and serious stares, this is the Duchess of Sussex unfiltered. Meghan Markle UNFILTERED: Photos reveal the moments we rarely see

BAFTA 2022 Film Awards: Rebel Wilson mocks Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's notorious Oprah Winfrey interview as she says it has everything from 'drama to fantasy' before taking aim at Prince Andrew Rebel Wilson made a jibe at Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's 2021 interview with Oprah Winfrey as she hosted the BAFTAs at the Royal Albert Hall in London on Sunday. BAFTA 2022 Film Awards: Rebel Wilson digs at Harry and Meghan

SARAH VINE: It's the poor Queen who is being punished by Prince Harry's diva drama SARAH VINE: Let me get this straight. Prince Harry will not be attending the memorial service for his late grandfather, the Duke of Edinburgh, on March 29. It's the poor Queen who is being punished by Prince Harry's drama

Meghan Markle and Prince Harry slam British Government for 'self-defeating nationalism, pharmaceutical monopolies and inequality' they say is behind failure to vaccinate poor countries against Covid The Duke and Duchess of Sussex are campaigning for Britain to work with pharmaceutical companies to waive intellectual property rights on the life-saving jabs. Meghan and Harry sign letter criticising Britain over covid jabs

Not his first rodeo? Prince Harry turns cowboy despite Meghan's love of animals - and more on this week's unmissable episode of our Palace Confidential royal chat show Speaking on the Mail's Palace Confidential, The Daily Mail's Diary Editor Richard Eden said Prince Harry's attendance at a Texas Rodeo could be part of his multimillion-pound media commitments. Prince Harry turns cowboy - and more on this week's royal chat show

Prince Harry is 'in regular contact with Prince Charles' but his relationship with Prince William 'has not recovered since Oprah interview', royal expert claims Writing in The Telegraph, royal expert Camilla Tominey questioned 'what the Duke and Duchess of Sussex have actually been doing' since they stepped down from life as senior royals last year. Prince Harry is 'in contact with Prince Charles', royal expert claims

A pre-wedding workout? Prince Harry's ex Chelsy Davy is spotted out for a jog wearing her dazzling sapphire ring - after it emerged she's welcomed a baby boy with a dashing Old Etonian hotelier The new mother, 36, who lives in London, opted for a pair of black leggings with sheer panels, navy hoodies and white running trainers as she stepped out with her pet in tow. Prince Harry's ex Chelsy Davy is spotted out for a jog wearing ring

Meghan will have a cow! Prince Harry has wild time at Texas rodeo - despite his wife's animal rights activism Prince Harry was spotted attending a Texas rodeo over the weekend - despite his wife's longtime animal rights activism. Prince Harry has wild time at Texas rodeo

Meghan will have a cow! Prince Harry has wild time at Texas rodeo - despite his wife's animal rights activism Prince Harry, 37, was pictured attending the Stockyards Rodeo event in Fort Worth on Saturday, surprising attendees who know of his wife, Meghan Markel's, years of animal rights activism. Prince Harry is slammed for attending a rodeo in Texas

Queen 'would desperately like to see' Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's baby daughter Lilibet in person, claims royal author The Queen, who has only seen Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's daughter via video link, is keen to meet her 11th great grandchild in the flesh, royal author Brian Hoey told The Express. The Queen 'desperately' wants to see Lilibet, claims royal author

TALK OF THE TOWN: Prince Harry's 'second dad' Mark Dyer receives warm welcome after returning home following cancer treatment TALK OF THE TOWN: Mark Dyer received a wonderfully warm welcome home, being showered with kisses from wife Amanda, on Mark's right in our picture, and family friend Natalie Pinkham. Prince Harry's 'second dad' Mark Dyer home after cancer treatment

Prince Harry and Meghan Markle hope to return to the UK as 'part-time royals' when Charles becomes King because he's more of a 'moderniser' than the Queen, royal author claims Speaking to the To Di For Daily podcast, royal author Tom Quinn said that Sussexes, who currently reside in California, hope to make a comeback in the future and spend six months in the UK. Harry and Meghan may want to return to the UK when Charles is king

Wedding bells for new mum Chelsy? Prince Harry's ex is spotted with a dazzling sapphire ring after it emerged she's welcomed a baby boy with a dashing Old Etonian hotelier New mother Chelsy, 36, was spotted with a dazzling sapphire ring as she ran errands in west London, days after it emerged she has welcomed a baby with Sam Cutmore-Scott. Prince Harry's ex Chelsy Davy is spotted with an engagement ring

Prince Harry is 'unlikely' to attend the Queen's Platinum Jubilee because he'll find it hard to face the royal family ahead of his bombshell memoirs Prince Harry was meant to come to the UK for his grandmother's Platinum Jubilee in June and a memorial service for his late grandfather in April. Prince Harry is 'unlikely' to attend the Queen's Platinum Jubilee

Prince Harry is 'unlikely' to attend the Queen's Platinum Jubilee because he'll find it hard to face the royal family ahead of his bombshell memoirs, royal biographer Tom Bower predicts The royal expert told Closer magazine that Prince Harry, 37, is unlikely to visit the UK this year to spend time with the Queen, 95, because of his potentially explosive memoirs about royal life. Prince Harry 'can't face his family' and won't come back, expert says

Meghan Markle supports British patronage Smart Works with a grant from her and Prince Harry's US-based Archewell Foundation to allow the charity to track female employment Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's Foundation Archewell will give out a grant to the Duchess of Sussex's longstanding patronage Smart Works to fund their research into female employment. Archewell will give a grant to Meghan Markle's patronage Smart Works

Hollywood Harry! Duke embraces singer Jennifer Hudson in behind-the-scenes snaps from NACCP awards as he proves he's settled into a life of mingling with America's A-list In snaps which have emerged on social media, the Duke of Sussex, 38, can be seen beaming as he chatted with the Dream Girls star backstage at the Hollywood event. Prince Harry embraces Jennifer Hudson in behind-the-scenes snaps

Hollywood Harry! Duke embraces singer Jennifer Hudson in behind-the-scenes snaps from NACCP awards as he proves he's settled into a life of mingling with the US A-list In snaps which have emerged on social media, the Duke of Sussex, 38, can be seen beaming as he chatted with the Dream Girls star backstage at the Hollywood event. Prince Harry embraces Jennifer Hudson in behind-the-scenes snaps

'Money driven' Harry and Meghan want 'MILLIONS,' expert claims Prince Harry and Meghan Markle are 'very driven by money' and would like to be earning 'millions' a year 'like their friend James Corden ', a royal expert has claimed. 'Money driven' Harry and Meghan want 'MILLIONS,' expert claims

'We stand with you': Harry and Meghan pay tribute to the people of Ukraine as they accept NAACP President's award for their 'distinguished public service' Prince Harry and Meghan Markle asked for the world to help support the Ukraine as they accepted the President's Award at the NAACP Image Awards on Saturday for their public service achievements. Harry and Meghan pay tribute to the people of Ukraine

Member of the Royal Family is set to visit Australia for the first time since Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's 2018 tour A member of the Royal Family will be visiting Australia for the first time since Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's 2018 tour. Member of Royal Family set to visit Australia

Family affair! Prince George, 8, joins rugby patrons Prince William and Kate Middleton as they go head-to-head in the stands as Wales takes on England in Six Nations tie The Duke and Duchess of Cambridge were joined by their eldest son Prince George - who cheekily poked his tongue out - during a rugby match. Prince George sticks his tongue out at rugby game with Will and Kate

Cheeky Prince George, eight, pokes his tongue out as he joins rugby patrons Prince William and Kate Middleton at England v Wales Six Nations match The Duke and Duchess of Cambridge were joined by their eldest son Prince George when attending England's Six Nations match against Wales this evening. Prince George joins Prince William and Kate at Six Nations tie

EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: Prince Harry's ex-girlfriend Chelsy Davy has 'secret baby boy' with mystery man after moving to a quiet area in West London EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: I hear the former City lawyer (pictured with Harry in 2006) gave birth to her first child last month without virtually anyone knowing she was pregnant. EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: Prince Harry's ex Chelsy Davy has 'secret baby boy'

Prince Harry says he was given 'insufficient information' over decision to change his tax-payer funded police bodyguards when he and Meghan are in the UK, High Court hears Prince Harry is bringing a legal challenge against the Home Office after being told he would no longer be given the 'same degree' of personal protective security when visiting the UK from the US. Harry given 'insufficient info' on security decision, court hears

EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: How Kate Middleton joined other school mums and popped to the pub for a drink RICHARD EDEN: Catherine was spotted relaxing over a drink with fellow parents of children at Thomas's school at the Hollywood Arms in Chelsea, one of Harry's old haunts. EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: How Kate Middleton popped to the pub for a drink

'Putin is shaking in his boots!': Twitter users remark on Harry and Meghan's defiant statement that they 'stand with the people of Ukraine' Prince Harry and Meghan Markle were ridiculed on social media today after intervening in the Ukraine crisis with a statement condemning Vladimir Putin's invasion. Prince Harry and Meghan Markle say they 'stand with' people of Ukraine

Pressure goes on the Queen to strip expat Prince Harry of his 'Counsellor of State' role but MPs are told disgraced Andrew should be STILL allowed to stand in for the monarch if she is incapacitated The House of Commons Library published guidance on what arrangements can be put in place if a monarch is unable to perform their royal duties and has said Harry should not be eligible to stand in. Queen could strip Harry of key role because he does not live in the UK

Revealed: Royal charity that partnered with Prince Harry's life coaching firm spent 98% of £796,000 cash it raised in one year on paying just TEN staff The Queen 's Commonwealth Trust (QCT) brought in £796,106 from donors but paid out £787,314 in staff costs to its ten employees in the 12 months to March 2021. Royal charity spent 98% of its cash paying 10 staff

Prince Harry renews soon-to-expire lease on Frogmore Cottage - making him still eligible to serve the Queen as a Counsellor because he has a UK address despite living in California The Duke of Sussex, who lives in California is eligible to continue serving his grandmother as one of her four Counsellors of State because he qualifies as being domiciled in Britain Prince Harry renews soon-to-expire lease on Frogmore Cottage

Prince Harry is expected to miss Philip's memorial service next month as he continues his legal battle over security On Friday, a court heard that Harry did not 'feel safe' in Britain without the protection of Scotland Yard officers, who he believes offer superior protection to privately hired bodyguards. Prince Harry is expected to miss Philip's memorial service

Why I demand a PROPER apology from my neighbour, the streaking Air Marshal: Businessman claims the RAF's second-in-command gave his family a VERY unwelcome fly-by... but is there more to the story than meets the eye? Nestling on the edge of the Chiltern Downs and just a short drive from the upmarket towns of Henley and Caversham, there are fewer more desirable places to live than the rural hamlet of Cane End. Why I demand a PROPER apology from the streaking Air Marshal

Controversial royal satire The Prince which mocked Prince George, 8, and Prince Philip is SCRAPPED by HBO after being slammed by viewers The Prince, which starred Prince Harry's friend Orlando Bloom and cost £5million to make, will not go forward for a second season, HBO's Chief Content Officer has said Casey Bloys told Deadline Royal satire which mocked Prince George and Prince Philip is SCRAPPED

Prince Harry could be interviewed by police in 'cash for honours' probe about his 'concern' over Saudi billionaire who was allegedly promised knighthood by Charles' aide The Duke of Sussex was accused of throwing his father under the bus after claiming he raised concerns about a Saudi billionaire donor. Charles' senior aide Michael Fawcett later quit. Prince Harry could be interviewed by police in cash for honours probe

Prince gets his hands on the prize: Maskless Harry clasps the Super Bowl trophy during his post-game visit to the Rams' locker room with billionaire owner Stan Kroenke…. but not all the players seem fussed Prince Harry made the most of his Los Angeles star power to get his hands on the Super Bowl trophy in the Rams' locker room on Sunday as he rubbed shoulders with their billionaire owner. Prince Harry pictured holding Super Bowl TROPHY in Rams' locker room

Prince Harry's bombshell book will 'shake the monarchy to the core' and lay bare feelings towards Camilla... as he STILL hasn't publicly congratulated his stepmother on being next Queen Friends of Prince Harry have warned his no-holds barred book will lay bare his true feelings toward his step-mother Camilla and is likely to 'shake the monarchy to its core'. Friends warn Prince Harry's book will 'shake the monarchy to the core'

Prince William and Prince Harry will 'both make compromises' and 'thrash out' their differences when they reunite for the Queen's Platinum Jubilee celebration, royal expert claims Vanity Fair's Katie Nicholl told the Birmingham Mail, the Duke of Cambridge and Duke of Sussex would be 'required' to appear alongside one another at the Jubilee celebrations. Prince William and Prince Harry will 'thrash it out', expert claims

'I curtsied in my track suit': Country singer Mickey Guyton shares a photo with 'lovely' Prince Harry at the Super Bowl following her National Anthem performance Mickey, 38, who opened the game on Sunday by singing the Star-Spangled Banner, called the Duke of Sussex, 37, 'lovely.' Harry donned black jeans, a white t-shirt, and a navy blue jacket. Mickey Guyton meets Prince Harry at Super Bowl after National Anthem

Why Princess Eugenie broke ranks to become the FIRST royal to visit Harry in LA after Megxit: Prince's closest ally in 'The Firm' joins him to watch Super Bowl Princess Eugenie has become the first member of the Royal Family to make a public visit to Prince Harry in California two years after he quit as a senior royal. Princess Eugenie becomes the FIRST royal to visit Harry in LA

Why Princess Eugenie broke ranks to become the FIRST royal to visit Harry in LA after Megxit: Prince's closest ally in 'The Firm' joins him to watch Super Bowl Prince Harry and Princess Eugenie sat in the premium seats at the SoFi Stadium in Los Angeles as concern mounts back in Britain over the Duke of Sussex's forthcoming tell-all biography. Super Bowl: Princess Eugenie visits Prince Harry in Los Angeles

Where's Meghan? Prince Harry and Princess Eugenie join Hollywood's royalty - including Kendall Jenner, Beyonce and Katy Perry - to watch the LA Rams triumph over Cincinnati Bengals in dramatic Super Bowl Prince Harry sat in the stands with Eugenie at the SoFi Stadium to see the Los Angeles Rams beat the Cincinnati Bengals 23-20 in a fourth-quarter comeback at Super Bowl LVI last night. Prince Harry attends Super Bowl with cousin Princess Eugenie
